        </td>
        <td width="50%">
            <b>M/S Renew Wind Energy (Rajasthan 2) Pvt. Ltd.,</b>
            <br><br><br><br>
            <div class="signature-area"></div>
            <b>Site Engineer</b><br><br>
            <b>Name of the site Engineer</b>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>

</body>
</html>